						<div class="vers-content">Men will be in love with self, in love with money, boastful, proud, abusive; without reverence for their parents, without gratitude, without scruple,</div>
					</div>
									<div id="vers178959" class="vers">
												<div class="vers-no">3</div>
						<div class="vers-content">without love, without peace; slanderers, incontinent, strangers to pity and to kindness;</div>
					</div>
