												<div class="vers-no">9</div>
						<div class="vers-content">yet they will come to little, they will soon be detected, like those others, in their rash folly.<a href="" class="inline-comment" data-comment-id="3347">âœ»</a> <span class="content-paragraph"><br><br></span></div>
					</div>
