						<div class="vers-content">Not such was the schooling, the guidance, thou hadst from me; in firm resolve, in faith, in patience, in love, in endurance;</div>
					</div>
									<div id="vers178967" class="vers">
												<div class="vers-no">11</div>
						<div class="vers-content">all my persecutions and suffering, such as those which befell me at Antioch, Iconium, and Lystra; what persecutions I underwent! And yet the Lord brought me through them all safely.</div>
					</div>
									<div id="vers178968" class="vers">
												<div class="vers-no">12</div>
						<div class="vers-content">And indeed, all those who are resolved to live a holy life in Christ Jesus will meet with persecution;</div>
					</div>
